sg":"下面仲有吳嘉熙對李施嬅,想投既話唔好錯過啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最後一輪甲組聯賽賽程:<br />\n<br />\n34.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-13<br />\n杜如風v陳逸敏<br />\n朱晨麗v車泳希<br />\n陳庭欣v朱茵<br />\n李施嬅v梁凱寧<br />\n黃智雯v梁嘉琪<br />\n陳華鑫v姚子羚<br />\n譚嘉儀(模)v吳嘉熙@SG<br />\n劉穎鏇v張沛樂<br />\n郭藹明v游蕙禎<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fd4505ef8e94c54087872cefd9ddf32b40c69e03","tid":654452,"uid":92376,"like":26,"dislike":83,"score":-57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-6 12:16am-10:16pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JFWqzXg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJFWqzXg.png&h=e5df4a05&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6Cz4cp2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Cz4cp2.png&h=e6bfc3fe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(14)吳嘉熙@SGvs李施嬅(4)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"c4c2cda1be7240562ca8bcf29d4dd5c7646ed9f3","tid":654452,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽已於4月29日舉行<br />\n冠軍由李佳芯奪得<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃決賽 5月27日凌晨0時<br />\n新垣結衣(日本)<br />\nvs<br />\nIU(韓國)<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4db7ebed3125291ce0f4b64da72c885c9bf70d3","tid":654452,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8b97eec65ec72f7d3c5c1cccc1caab0b256435","tid":654452,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"投左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc5646a2e8c8cedb82a2811e4fa5d7c80be58ef","tid":654452,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8b97eec65ec72f7d3c5c1cccc1caab0b256435","tid":654452,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"投左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfd46c5ad756a11a5d00c8ccadd542facd3ab25","tid":654452,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T18:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b953e4ab6273c2c4515dcb43da8a70103bbd35","tid":654452,"uid":15